description:
My house locates outside the Savin Hill station (Red line ) . Perfect location to stay if you would like to visit Boston by subway .

The space
We are just downside of the T ( red line @ Savin hill ) . 1 minuets walk to T; 10-15 minutes (4 -5 stops ) to South Station & Downtown; 20-25 minuets (8-9) stops to MIT & Harvard.
Easy and fast come and go from Logan airport ( free when come from airport)

Guest access
You can use our kitchen as your own. Help yourself to enjoy various food such as milk, juice, bread, cup noodle, egg, cereal, etc.

Other things to note
Need to share bathroom with other Airbnb guests
